item.description:
I’m a graduate student at UIC, currently pursuing a Masters in Management Information Systems at University of Illinois, Chicago with a focus on Data Science & Analytics. I am very passionate about numbers and statistics and have worked on several projects in Data Science where I have tried leveraging Machine Learning & Statistics to design data-driven solutions to some exciting real-world problems.

Interests

  • Data Science
  • Machine Learning
  • Statistics
  • Healthcare Analytics
